Package org.eclipse.mat.inspections

Class ReferenceQuery

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mat.inspections.ReferenceQuery
All Implemented Interfaces:
IQuery
public class ReferenceQuery extends Object implements IQuery
Extract information about objects extending java.lang.ref.Reference, e.g. weak and soft references, and Finalizer.
